Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:09.85,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.50,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've woken you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.62,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my carelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.21,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The dream the Miss drew for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:28.74,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving this place to raise a flag of justice there;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:33.21,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,calling in members of the group\nand taking on the city of villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.45,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we have seen how skilled these Russian soldiers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:46.83,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will cut a path through them\nand challenge Balalaika one on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:50.65,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is certainly worthy of this white scabbard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.84,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far with you, Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:58.66,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be with you from now on as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.66,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even to Roanapur?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.16,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.99,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:21.70,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, our job here will end without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:23.36,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My job ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:27.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from Moscow will take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:32.86,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame I won't get to see the aftermath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.49,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.36,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ishiguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those three that came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.53,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.90,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not "oh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:57.07,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The two Caucasians and one Japanese\nthat came in here, did you look into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:01.17,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having someone check the ICPO data,\nbut I haven't got anything-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:04.11,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about having an international specialist come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:07.68,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Someone named Kouno is supposed to be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:13.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That white woman is definitely involved in the war\nbetween the Washimine Group and the Kousa Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe even the Adachi bowling center\nshooting incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.99,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? Don't take your eyes off of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.86,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.20,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:33.37,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who looked like you had something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.36,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:38.92,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Balalaika...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:42.43,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, are you going to keep talking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:47.64,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've already saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:52.44,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:54.44,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to simply wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.16,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to simply listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:00.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:03.33,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about to end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.80,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,before that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.58,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to completely crush the Washimine Group
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.84,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,until the survival of the group becomes impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.84,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Without leaving a single withered tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.59,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only that can free her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.89,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:29.42,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:36.90,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only method\nto push the princess back into a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.66,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a villain, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.91,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was the correct decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:50.54,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become a good villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.71,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.42,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain you must be tired from these long discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:05.53,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it.\NThis accomplishes one of our goals as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wipe the slate clean and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.77,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:21.34,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We must prepare plans on who will succeed us,\nin the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.27,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:29.91,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If certain contingencies should occur in our absence,\nit will be difficult for us to respond properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:36.41,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to know your state of readiness over firearms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.07,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it too loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:50.10,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but compared to other groups, we have many more guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.93,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've even purchased machine guns\nfrom the guys in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.60,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you oblige me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.27,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morozumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.92,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see the bullets as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.60,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's quite a competent bodyguard you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.54,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a secondary firearm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.04,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.97,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no profit in having a shoot-out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.97,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a pain later. Give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.69,black lagoon regular,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:48.68,black lagoon regular,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely atrocious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.55,black lagoon regular,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up with me, okay Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.79,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a atrocious gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:58.07,black lagoon regular,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look, sergeant... Atrocious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.31,black lagoon alternative,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Atrocious isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.14,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt if even low life punks in the gutter\nwould use guns like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.21,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely atrocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.82,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a hideous gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.18,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever stopped to consider,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:19.10,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,what it would feel like to be shot with a gun like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.00,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:30.91,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't work with scum\nwho shamelessly sport shoddy guns like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.62,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yasuda! Gun shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Enter the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.62,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.49,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.62,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.75,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or we'll force our way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:57.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This gun isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.87,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, how are we on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.43,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is not an issue, Kapitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.47,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we explain this to the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:07.98,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to make war and burn it all to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.95,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I simply followed orders obediently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.20,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.65,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.82,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want it as a souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.08,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't carry things I'm not accustomed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:20.58,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:26.36,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will not forget that I pulled this trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.38,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.94,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, throw that gun away here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:37.01,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're returning to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.48,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.94,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yasuda of the fourth precinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:48.38,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ishikawa of the 1st precinct.\NI'm in charge of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.07,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear about the gun shots earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.49,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How are we on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.05,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.59,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, give this message to the Washimine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:05.42,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Moscow will cease all attacks as of this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:11.94,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Washimine Group you seek to destroy\nhas already dispersed underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.43,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That girl thinks more flexibly than you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:21.98,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,According to the information Bulgazivi gathered,\ntheir group members believe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:28.42,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,that their princess will invite them\nto Roanapur to raise their flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.82,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roanapur of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.70,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My ride is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.58,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open a path, civilian policemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.10,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm not done...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.13,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.65,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ambassador is waiting at the Mamiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.91,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vlatinera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:53.81,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.84,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Mr. Yasuda. It's a foreign plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:03.56,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:04.89,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:05.23,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:06.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.09,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.27,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.83,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones you have business with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.30,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so easily distracted by small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.84,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell Mr. Civilian Cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:28.01,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever need me, come by the CIS embassy any time.\NIt's V. N. Vasilinov.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.58,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.16,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I didn't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.83,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kouno with International Investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:45.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you arrest them, if you witnessed gun shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.44,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred inside, we only had assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:53.21,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that? Did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.28,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.78,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They have their base of operations in Moscow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,they even have a strong foothold in Chechnya and New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:03.08,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The powerful Mafia organization called Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's known as Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's a high ranking officer in Hotel Moscow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.52,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.12,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:12.59,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.86,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The scene of the incident to Center!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.90,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Send a message to all PCs in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.16,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a photograph of her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:19.20,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a description of her appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.17,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:24.62,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll at least find out her contacts within Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.15,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We need to tell her that the war's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.45,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.86,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In just over thirty minutes\nthis place is going to be quarantined!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.36,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.69,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Contact them from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.95,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're close to departure time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.57,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.06,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please escort us to the Maria Zeleska.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.34,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.30,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:23.78,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.70,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's been kidnapped by a high school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.64,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You drive too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.61,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a delinquent, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:39.15,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio, what was that act about taking Roanapur?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.26,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing in the twilight, just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.26,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there are some things I can see because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.35,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.19,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Moscow announced an end to fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.59,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:55.13,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of promise is Balalaika's word?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.10,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:03.91,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can anyone trust that rabid dog that\nbreaks all promises, betrays you, and spits on faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.95,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.28,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:23.76,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I could honestly believe that I could recreate the\ngroup in Roanapur, that would have been wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.23,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it was just a passing wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.18,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Gin and I are here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:32.67,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the Washimine and our emblem exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.23,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has not been grounded yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.44,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you keep coming back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:41.04,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, I was born into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.40,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up with the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.68,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've enjoyed pretending and playing on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:50.05,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, this is the path of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:53.58,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no value as a hostage against Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.99,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:13:00.49,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I'd like you to witness how this ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.80,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only a massacre is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a flower that may bloom there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.77,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.40,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We are Yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.51,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, the operation is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us return to Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.37,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.04,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:41.19,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be the ones to break first in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.26,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.73,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.59,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! She's already the walking dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:09.06,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.70,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Kousa Council\nwas destroyed due to internal discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:20.71,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, the one who betrayed and slaughtered\NBando Tsugio, our group's leader, still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The head of our enemy Hotel Moscow, Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.98,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Living with honor, seeing justice through,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.15,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to reward honor is our pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.22,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is no duty that you must be bound by!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:33.89,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a front!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:40.09,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please open the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.15,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gin is no longer with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:14.28,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have brought the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:18.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.29,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far we go, we're not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:26.23,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a place only those like us should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.63,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.71,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:37.44,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was a way in which you could have\navoided ending up like Miss Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.14,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would choose that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.65,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.79,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here to save face as Yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:55.11,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You struggled against being absorbed into the night.\NThat's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:06.11,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Standing here in the twilight, there are things I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:10.24,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should have Gin throw away his sword\nand run away with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.45,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Become wanderers together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.64,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,seeking a far-off land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.25,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a joke as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.63,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.98,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the real you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.67,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are times I wonder,\N"What if I were able to live like that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.81,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the die is already cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:46.28,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've always quietly wished\nthat life in Takamachi would go on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.38,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the trees and stores up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:53.46,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That it'd be fun with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.21,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.97,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is too damn late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.66,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only place we end up is in a coffin of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:22.48,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.66,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've blundered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.33,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.26,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.84,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was looking a little black,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:41.44,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but you made her say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.85,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was your real bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.71,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for that, I'd be the one on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.71,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.85,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.74,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your leg up Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.34,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rewrap it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:00.78,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:06.32,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why has it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:14.07,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were warped,\nby lying to yourself that you wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:19.27,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were too smart to fool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.47,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:27.81,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven people have been killed on my orders\nsince that night I threw the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:31.31,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our city is full of people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.73,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've woken up, it's much too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.95,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That land...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.93,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for having troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.83,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring everything to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.70,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at her, Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.33,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.12,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.22,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I haven't seen you in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:15.30,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How was that fake Chinese passport I got you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.98,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was it useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.49,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.90,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:26.95,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People are like dice, we throw ourselves into life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:30.51,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the Frenchman who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.48,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jean-Paul Sartre.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.46,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An existentialist philosopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:43.30,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I prefer, "Quickly put a hole in a guy\nwho tries to put five eggs into three baskets."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.06,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.03,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.13,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's work as soon as you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:54.00,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They want a us to deliver a pile of guns\nby the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.64,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.79,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for our flight, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:20.55,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From Miss Balalaika for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.57,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In this city, Roanapur,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.53,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,by the power of guns and liquor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:30.33,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,there's a wonderful place where you can\nblow anything away through barbaric power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:32.37,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not such a bad place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.73,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm beginning to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:36.17,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:42.71,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it all through from the twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.72,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.77,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Into our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:51.81,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And? How was Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:55.59,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Balalaika was there and we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:57.32,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:58.49,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:00.39,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking about Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.30,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You two were away together for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:05.08,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did do it this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:07.56,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:14.50,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.61,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:23.15,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We villains don't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:23.39,black lagoon regular,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bang.
